                                    class="text-warning material-icons md-qr_code"></i></span>
                            <div class="text">
                                <h6 class="mb-1 card-title"><img style="width: 100px; height: 80px;margin-right: 15px;"
                                        class="img-fluid"
                                        src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/wearable-technology-isometric-flowchart_1284-19018.jpg?size=626&ext=jpg&uid=R95547652&semt=sph"
